  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/69194538ff4aa492ef081c1b815f7441.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" width=616 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/69194538ff4aa492ef081c1b815f7441.webm?t=1766115800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/69194538ff4aa492ef081c1b815f7441.mp4?t=1766115800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>~ Baby ducklings have been kidnapped, and you are a very angry Mama Duck.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a QuackMan Roguelite. Battle the evil Lich and his undead minions to rescue your ducklings. Classic PacMan controls but with an added ATTACK button that can destroy walls and vanquish enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/9644932f4ee44a0280fa7074a33617c4.webp?t=1766115800\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/49cc7d72c23cd45028ff1a91e745671b.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/49cc7d72c23cd45028ff1a91e745671b.webm?t=1766115800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/49cc7d72c23cd45028ff1a91e745671b.mp4?t=1766115800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\