\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/01ced91920d0429c35c8efb3783fa73e.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" class=\"bb_img\" width=55 height=20 /></picture></span> <strong><u>Gameplay:</u></strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/01ced91920d0429c35c8efb3783fa73e.apng?t=1766115800\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/01ced91920d0429c35c8efb3783fa73e.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" class=\"bb_img\" width=55 height=20 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Mama Duck and navigate your way through the evil Lich's dungeon maze. Rescue your lost ducklings and form a giant chain of ducks. You must battle waves of undead minions. In this adorable QuackMan Roguelite, you can customize Mama Duck with hundreds of different gear combinations. Your gear gives unique active and passive abilities. They are also adorable accessories, so you can fashion up your duck.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" width=80 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.webm?t=1766115800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" width=80 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.webm?t=1766115800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" width=80 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.webm?t=1766115800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" width=80 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.webm?t=1766115800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" width=80 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.webm?t=1766115800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" width=80 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.webm?t=1766115800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" width=80 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/785f71c38ac5b881714207c8ffeb0b36.webm?t=1766115800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><u>Features:</u></strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/3db799ec075e079a65ac39cbd5356818.webp?t=1766115800\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/3db799ec075e079a65ac39cbd5356818.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=20 /></picture></span>  Destroy walls and make your own path through the maze!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/3db799ec075e079a65ac39cbd5356818.webp?t=1766115800\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/3db799ec075e079a65ac39cbd5356818.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=20 /></picture></span>  Battle massive bosses and fight back a wide variety of undead minions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/3db799ec075e079a65ac39cbd5356818.webp?t=1766115800\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/3db799ec075e079a65ac39cbd5356818.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=20 /></picture></span>  Make animal friends, like the shop cat at Toe Beans Cafe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/3db799ec075e079a65ac39cbd5356818.webp?t=1766115800\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/3db799ec075e079a65ac39cbd5356818.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=20 /></picture></span> Meta upgrades and progression.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/3db799ec075e079a65ac39cbd5356818.webp?t=1766115800\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898900/extras/3db799ec075e079a65ac39cbd5356818.poster.avif?t=1766115800\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=20 /></picture></span>  FASHION DUCKS! Hundreds of gear combinations for Mama Duck </p></li></ul>",
